Module kbaldr2.main
Package kbaldr2.model

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
kbaldr2.model.DataCache
kbaldr2.model.Appointment
public class Appointment extends DataCache
Represents an appointment, extending the DataCache class. Contains appointment-specific data such as title, description, location, type, start and end date times, customer, user, and contact.
